------------------------------------------------------
jvCard 0.9

Author: Thilo Brandt (mail@thilo-brandt.de)
------------------------------------------------------

A vCard 3.0 java library for parsing and creating of vCards

This github repository contains the source files and build infrastructure of jvCard 0.9. 

-----
Required Software for building/compiling jvCard 0.9:

Java JDK 1.5+ (http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html)

Apache Ant 1.8+ (http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi) 

-----
Build process:

There is a default target "distribute" defined in the central build.xml file, which publishes this jvCard library as JAR file to the ./dist/<date>/lib/ directory

Recommended target commands:

bash>ant

or

bash>ant distribute

For JavaDoc generation use 

bash>ant javadoc
